==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tabellion
<hw>Ta*bel"lion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tabellio</ets>, fr. <ets>tabella</ets> a tablet, a writing,
document, dim. of <ets>tabula</ets> a board: cf. F.
<ets>tabellion</ets>. See <er>Table</er>.]</ety> <def>A secretary or
notary under the Roman empire; also, a similar officer in France during
the old monarchy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

